descriptionHtml:
Today I am happy to announce that Skyrim MV is under development.

Skyrim MV is a Fan-made classic RPG made by using RPG maker MV with graphic, sound and community script. The game is based on The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim by Bethesda Softworks. It is a commercial free project for those who love the Skyrim universe as much as I do. Skyrim MV is currently under development and there's no future release date yet. At the mean time you are welcome to go on my website or Youtube Channel leave some commend and feedback.

Thank you.
